    "LLMs can take decisions but they might change their opinions when we ask the same questions in repetition, this is because they are trained on a fixed set of data sets which can be outdated and lack the intelligence we as humans exhibit in [these] scenarios.",
    "4.1.5 Scaffolding that allows focus on critical thinking.",
    "Overall, students seemed to have a fairly positive experience using an LLM as a discussion partner, even if they were aware of its limitations.",
